  "description": "A wide shot captures the iconic Golden Gate Bridge spanning a body of water, likely the San Francisco Bay. The bridge is a vibrant orange-red color and stands out against the deep blue of the water and the bright blue sky. Gentle ripples cover the water's surface. On either side of the waterway, hilly landscapes covered in lush green vegetation frame the scene, creating a sense of depth and scale. The sky is a clear, bright blue with a few wispy clouds, suggesting a sunny day. The composition is balanced, with the bridge centrally positioned and the surrounding landscape providing a natural frame.",
